---
title: Unbeatable Beef Rump & Corn Rice Bowl with Slaw, Pickled Cucumber & Smokey Aioli
description: This dish is a true feast for champions! Tender, juicy and perfectly cooked beef rump is the crowning glory, sitting atop fluffy jasmine rice speckled with sweetcorn. A colourful slaw and tangy quick-pickled cucumber cut through the richness of the steak, creating a balanced meal fit for a king.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
